Install dart and Flutter extension.
Press ctl + shift + p -> Flutter new project
Enter a name and choose location, project will be created.
Install android studio and create an emulator (prefer nexus 6 with pie android)
than run flutter run or press F5 on main.dart

User provider for state management in flutter.
https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=j_SJ7XmT2MM&list=PL4cUxeGkcC9j--TKIdkb3ISfRbJeJYQwC&index=8